=F0=9F=93=B1Mobile push notifications
* You will get a push message on mobile when someone mentions you=2C invit=
es you to a page=2C or changes your permissions

=F0=9F=94=97 iOS and Android Share to now support the system photo gallery
* Add images from your phone=E2=80=99s gallery to AppFlowy

=F0=9F=9A=80 Document improvements
* Table of Contents gets a new look with customizable background colors
* Code
+ Introduces new features: pin language=2C add captions=2C Ask AI=2C and t=
urn text into code
+ Includes bug fixes: support plain text=2C disabled shortcuts=2C and more=
 languages
* Callout is improved with a more polished UI and quick styles

=F0=9F=94=A5 Upcoming releases:
* AI Meeting Notes & AI Audio Transcription
* Toggle=2C Equation=2C and right-click menu improvements with bug fixes
* Page version history: restore to an older version

Until next time=2C

